				<div class="hvres-header">			<div class="hvres-definition no-word">			<p class="hvres-spell"><a href="/hv/hiệt">hiệt</a><span class="hvres-operations"> <i class="fas fa-link icon icon-hoverable" data-tippy-content="Copy liên kết" onclick="CopyURLToClipboard(location.origin+'/whv/絜#pl9069bd7033')"></i></span>			</p>			<p class="hvres-info gray small">phồn & giản thể</p>			</div>
